support asicminer block erupter on openwrt

How to build
1. prepare an openwrt enviroment
2. cd to openwrt directory
3. clone this repo and cgminer folder to openwrt/package
4. run script by ./script/feeds update -a
5. run script by ./script/feeds install -a
6. make menuconfig
   select cgminer in utility
7. make j=4
8. the openwrt compile environment will generate all the thing you need. You can find cgminer in ipk format in package folder


How to run:
cgminer -o pooladdress -u userid -p passwd --usb ICA:1
